This correspondence serves as final confirmation of your registration for this paper-based testing examination and details are as follows: Your Name As It Should Appear On Your Government Issued Identification: Fei Gao Your PMI Eligibility ID 6983747E3 Exam Project Management Professional (PMP)® First Language/Language Aid English/Simplified Chinese Exam Date and Time 14:30 PM, Nov 27, 2022 Test Site Code 1360 Test Site Address Shenzhen Vocational and Technical College (Xilihu Campus), No.4089 West Shahe Road, Nanshan District, Shenzhen, Guangdong Xilihu Campus, Shenzhen Vocational and Technical College, 4089 Shahe West Road, Nanshan District, Shenzhen City, Guangdong Province Contact Person Sun, Xiling 400 1628 768 sunnypmp@sztc.org All candidates are strongly recommended to arrive at the test site before 14:00 pm on the date of the examination for registration.
